title: File:Suburban Yangon (8446426678).jpg
author: Marcel Oosterwijk from Amsterdam, The Netherlands
description:
To all people who want to visit Myanmar: please DO NOT GO to government owned hotels and avoid large resorts. The resorts are mostly build there by foreign companies interested only in money making. Local fishermen have nowhere to go in a few years because the beach looks like a second – overcrowded – Thailand by then.

See also: <a href="http://www.lonelyplanet.com/myanmar-burma/travel-tips-and-articles/76954" rel="noreferrer nofollow">www.lonelyplanet.com/myanmar-burma/travel-tips-and-articl...</a>
